headline: Jacobs Selected as Program Manager for the New Dallas Pediatric Campus
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was selected as the owner's program manager for a groundbreaking hospital project by a joint venture between Children's Health and the University of Texas (UT) Southwestern Medical Center. Located in Dallas, Texas, the new pediatric campus will help revolutionize healthcare with state-of-the-art, patient-centric facilities designed to meet increasing needs in one of the nation's fastest growing metropolitan regions.
